cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper applies Deep Learning techniques to the problem of precipitation nowcasting, which involves processing radar images. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of DL implies that the paper may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with weather prediction, which could fall under the Geometric Representation (cs.GR) sub-category.
